            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Genesis Global School has been a game-changer for my child! The nurturing environment and dedicated teachers have helped them develop not only academically but also emotionally. The school's focus on self growth, personality development and creativity has enabled my child to enhance their inner skills, such as:\n\n- Confidence: They've become more self-assured and willing to take on new challenges.\n- Creativity: They've discovered new talents and interests, and their imagination has flourished.\n- Empathy: They've learned to understand and appreciate different perspectives, becoming a compassionate and caring individual.\n- Resilience: They've developed coping skills and perseverance, helping them navigate obstacles with ease.\n\nThe school's commitment to holistic growth has been instrumental in unlocking my child's full potential. I'm grateful for the supportive community and exceptional education they receive.\"",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
